Add these to a .gitignore file in your repository root: 

# Vitis generated files
.metadata/
.settings/
Debug/
Release/
build/
_ide/
*.log
*.elf
*.bin
*.bit
*.pdi
*.zip

# Ignore specific component files if they have absolute paths
# (You may need to track these if you fixed them to be relative)
# vitis-comp.json
# app.yaml
